123f","tid":2205142,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fd36931d9831f09d5b4b20f477e1b436255e902b","tid":2205142,"uid":229057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T19:52:27.000Z","msg":"葵芳張謙昌醫生好work <br />\n由細到大都有濕疹<br />\n最嚴重個時手腳摺位 面 頸 頭皮 耳仔 手碗都有<br />\n睇左佢兩次之後就好返哂<br />\n到而家已經斷咗尾三四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:00:30.000Z","msg":"佢開藥定點？"}]}